    {# Claims procss #}
    <section class="section--pad homepage--claims-process">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="h1 text-blue">Our hassle-free claims process...</h2>
            <p class="lead">When something bad happens to your phone:</p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="large-no large-no--arrow">1</span>
                    <h4 class="h3 text-blue">Contact Claims Team</h4>
                    <p>Let us know what happened. You can do this by <a href="{{ path('claim') }}" class="text-nowrap"><strong>filling in this form</strong></a>, or <strong>calling our claims team on 0344 856 0852</strong> <small>(local rates apply)</small></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="large-no large-no--arrow">2</span>
                    <h4 class="h3 text-blue">Review Claim</h4>
                    <p>Our UK based claims team will review your claim and reach out with a request for any further details or documents (if necessary). <strong>We aim to do this within a matter of hours during UK business hours</strong>.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="large-no">3</span>
                    <h4 class="h3 text-blue">Approve Claim</h4>
                    <p>Once your claim is approved, we take your excess payment over the phone and aim to <strong>get a replacement phone in the next working day</strong>. If you prefer to have your phone repaired, it may take more time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

